<h3>OUR STORY</h3>
<p style="white-space: pre-wrap;">It all started in the summer of 2021 when Ryan asked Angela out on their first date to his favorite roast beef spot in town. It was a Monday night so the date was expected to be a short one but as Nicks was closing down, neither wanted the date to end. So they walked around the neighborhood until they found a bar that was open and shot some pool. After closing that place down as well, they parted ways but soon after were inseparable, spending all their free time together.

  They enjoyed camping, cooking, concerts, eating out, traveling, spending time with family/friends and taking Bella on long walks. They moved in together spring of 2022 and 8 months later he proposed!</p>

